aca.org/taxonomy/repentance"/>Repentance</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/saints.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/saints"/>Saints</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/shame.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/shame"/>Shame</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/sin.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/sin"/>Sin</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/sleep.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/sleep"/>Sleep</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/water.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/water"/>Water</a></li><li><a href="/aggregate/taxonomy/wine.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/taxonomy/wine"/>Wine</a></li></ul><h4>Related person(s)</h4><ul><li><a href="/aggregate/person/74.html"><span class="loadRDF getLabel" data-rdfRef="http://syriaca.org/person/74"/>
